<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Abnormal Lab Readings Alert</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .patient { margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; }
        .patient-header { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .observation { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .observation-header { font-weight: bold; }
        .abnormal { color: #d9534f; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Abnormal Lab Readings Alert</h1>
    <p>The following abnormal lab readings were detected:</p>

    {{#each abnormalResults}}
    <div class="patient">
        <div class="patient-header">
            <h2>Patient: {{patientName}} (ID: {{patientId}})</h2>
        </div>
        <h3>Abnormal Observations:</h3>
        {{#each abnormalObservations}}
        <div class="observation">
            <p class="observation-header">{{display}} ({{code}})</p>
            <p>Value: <span class="abnormal">{{value}} {{unit}}</span></p>
            <p>Interpretation: {{interpretation}}</p>
            <p>Reference Range: {{referenceRange}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{/each}}

    <p>Please review these results and take appropriate action as necessary.</p>
    <p>This is an automated message. Do not reply to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>